{"word":"G4920 - συνίημι - syníēmi - soon-ee'-ay-mee - Consider","slug":"G4920","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνίημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>syníēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-ee'-ay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consider"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BD;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - sunie&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>soon-ee'-ay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <b>&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>hie&#x0304;mi</b> (to <i>send</i>); to <i>put together</i>, that is, (mentally) to <i>comprehend</i>; by implication to <i>act piously:</i> - consider, understand, be wise."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4907\">G4907</a>, <a href=\"#/G4908\">G4908</a>, <a href=\"#/G801\">G801</a>"}]}